data.title: Aggressive Aftershock Mid Combo From Cat
data.description: Here's a strong, but simple way to contest for Mid control from Cat. It is recommended to coordinate this play with your teammates Bottom Mid.

data.title: Early Aggressive B Main Control Stun + Flash From Lane
data.description: Enable your teammates successfully with this combination of utility, as it will disrupt any Attacker from contesting B Main control.
